originalText.text: Best acupuncturist ever. She cures everything. She has the biggest heart in the world. The kindest, most amazing person ever. I was on 4 rounds of antibiotics for an infection that would not go away. Within one dose of herbs, I had no more symptoms. By 2 days infection was gone. Miracle worker! I have been going to her for over 10 years. She cures everything big and small.
